“So what are you going to do now?” asked Blaise.
Draco shrugged. “I suppose I’m going to marry Granger.”
His friends exchanged glances with each other.
“And you… don’t mind that?” asked Theo carefully. “I know what you told Lucius, but you
can be honest with us.”
Draco considered this. “No, I don’t mind it. I was entirely honest. She’s very…
