Theo lit up at this. “What were her recommendations then?”
Draco opened his mouth to respond, but was cut off by Pansy shoving her husband lightly.
“Not now Theo. I need to hear more about this.”
She turned back to Draco. “So what… you two are friends now? Is that it?”
Draco shrugged. “Not really, but I don’t think we’re enemies anymore either. She referred to
