“Detente,” said Pansy skeptically.
“Yes, detente,” agreed Draco. “Not friends, but not enemies either.”
“So all that shit she said during the Matching Ceremony…” began Blaise.
Draco felt a lurch of embarrassment.
“She was speaking in hypotheticals,” he said quietly, as he turned to stare out the window.
“I’ve never thought about it very much, but I suspect she is correct about all of it. The MLPP
practically encourages spousal rape, doesn’t it? And it could put somebody like her in a very
