“And your parents?” asked Pansy.
Draco hesitated.
“Tell us, Draco,” said Pansy. “I think we need to know.”
Draco sighed. “Yes, they watched too. In fact, they argued with Bella over who would get to
turn over Potter to the Dark Lord. And I think Bella offered Granger to Grayback if memory
