“We’re doing a very short version in the interest of time,” said Goldstein.
They both nodded.
“Draco Malfoy,” continued Goldstein, as he looked at Draco. “Do you consent to this
marriage?”
“I do,” said Draco firmly.
“And Hermione Granger, do you consent to this marriage?” asked Goldstein.
Involuntarily Draco’s stomach clenched. This was where it had all gone wrong three months
ago.
“I do,” she said, with a small smile on her face.
Draco couldn’t help but smile broadly at that. Goldstein placed his wand on their joined
