betraying over a decade of friendship with me for what? A guaranteed shag? I’ve never slept
with you Ronald, and after years of turning you down whenever you tried I thought you
would take a bloody hint!”
FLASH!
This time the cameraman was aiming at Weasley’s face. He was gaping at Granger.
“Ms. Skeeter!” cried Shacklebolt.
“Ah ah ah Minister,” she tutted. “No closed sessions here. This is public property and very
newsworthy.”
Shacklebolt looked around a bit desperately. There were a couple of aurors behind him,
along with the small wizard Draco recognized from the Matching Ceremony. The aurors
