“At least he was honest!” she screeched, and Draco winced a bit at the pitch of her voice.
“An honest Death Eater! How fucking rich is that? And do you know what? He was the
only one who told me the truth about what was going on out there! He was the only one who
visited me without any false pretenses! He told me on his very first visit that he wanted to
marry me, and he’s been coming back for months to persuade me! I’m not saying this is
