Protect her. Make sure her children are yours. Claim her.
The aurors drew their wands as one, but Draco held up a hand to stop them.
“It’s just the Malfoy magic,” he said calmly. “She is my wife, and she can’t be touched.”
Then he looked down at Weasley. “The next time you lay a hand on another wizard’s wife,
you’d do well to remember that not all family magic functions like yours. She has made it
very clear that she doesn’t want you touching her, and thanks to you I’m now the only man
