Then he squeezed Granger’s hand again.
“Allow me,” he said, as he turned and apparated them directly into the hotel room Draco had
reserved for them.
“Here?” she asked, looking around. He saw her eyes sweeping over the small bag Potter had
put together for her and the camp bed on one side of the room, as far away from the real bed
