Draco stared at her in disbelief. “Rita wasn’t warded out?”
Granger shrugged. “The house is warded, but the last time I was there the wards had been
loosened around the grounds for the press due to the wedding. Maybe they forgot to put
them back in place.”
“Bloody hell, that’s incredible,” said Draco, leaning back to relish the thought.
“Even better,” added Granger, now with a distinct sparkle in her eye, “Ron was arrested with
his pants down, though Prudence was completely dressed.”
