“It’s true,” she acknowledged. “It’s a shitshow.”
“A shitshow of Weasley’s own making though,” pointed out Draco.
Hermione inclined her head in acknowledgment just as Patsy popped in.
“Mistress,” she said, addressing Hermione, “there is a mediwitch at the gate requesting your
