“And we will also sue you for assault,” added Draco.
Granger turned to look at him, and he smiled to see the approval on her face.
“Yes, that too. And I will be writing about it in The Daily Prophet,” she added.
The mediwitch swallowed, but finally nodded and rose. “Very well. I will… communicate
